What is Date class in Java and why do we use it?
    - Date class is a way we can get the current time, date in multiple different forms.

    FORMATS
    yyyy-MM-dd -> 2021-07-15
    MM/dd/yyyy -> 07/15/2021
    dd-MMM-yyyy ->  15-Jul-2021
    E, MMM dd yyyy -> Thu, Jul 15 2021
    hh:mm:ss a -> 08:33:27 PM
    h:mm a  ->  8:37 PM
    EEE  ->  Thu
    EEEE  ->  Thursday